title: Where Were You When JFK Was Shot
description:
3 x 15 mins

All of us remember where we were when the news of JFK's assassination came through. I was only a child at the time, but remember where I was - with my Mother - and the impact the news had on the adults around me.

This set of three short stories take this day as their basis and the way in which people's lives were impacted by events in their own lives that day. An interesting and thoughtful trio.
